snippet.title: The Flames that Follow Us - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Flames that Follow Us is a brutal melee-combat game about overcoming impostor syndrome. 
Download: https://vanandrew.itch.io/flames

A game by Van Andrew Nguyen, with music from Toby Wu and Rosentwig.


Trailer song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GUO3N0W1WGY
Additional Links: https://linktr.ee/vanandrewdev
